	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qua fide accipiuntur et reddantur hoc pessimo saeculo literę, <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingere</persName> frater et compater in domino charissime, experiuntur boni viri plus satis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De commentariis meis in ambas apostoli ad Corinthios epistolas deque strena missa <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p2207">Heinricho</persName>, filiolo nostro, iam dudum ad te scripsi; verum cui commissae fuerint eę literae, recordari nequeo senili vicio impeditus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi item abs te, quae in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l619" cert="high">Bavaricae</placeName> examinationis articulos aedidisti, quos et <persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Melanchthonem</persName> in publicis lectionibus perstrinxisse accepi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raro quidem scribo, fateor; sed cogitandum est amicis, quam sit senectus torpida ac tarda, illique condonandum, si quid officii desyderatur, id quod te quoque facere non dubito.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Legi, quae ad d. <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerum</persName> compatrem meum de disputatione sacramentaria scripsisti, quae habita est in academia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l210" cert="high">Heidelbergensi</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oro dominum, ut, quod fęliciter coeptum est, provehatur quoque fęliciter.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid ea de re certius adhuc acceperis, oro, communices.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quodsi princeps elector pius est et veritatis amans, cogito de Locis meis illi nuncupandis idque certas ob causas, qua in re iuvare me poteris.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3429" cert="high">Vireti</persName> exasperatio nihil efficiet aliud, quam ut ipsius corculum acerbitate propria adhuc amplius corrodatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Concedendum non est, quod existimat ecclesiam Christi esse non posse, quae non sit secundum conceptam ab ipsis disciplinam instituta.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed hoc tu melius.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Optime vale, compater charissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Bibliandrum</persName>, <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Petrum Martyrem</persName>, <persName ref="p2336" cert="high">Bernardinum</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8011" cert="high">Waltherum</persName> et reliquos una cum domu tua.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutat te filiolus tuus <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p487">Heinrichus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 59., 12. iunii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo theologo m. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, compatri suo in domino longe charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
